      "text": "It's a holdover from the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAmarisCivilWar],Amaris Civil War]]. There was a great battle in orbit over Panzyr, and most of the wreckage is still there in the form of a dense field of particulate material.\n\nNavigating the field unassisted would be a formidable task. Thankfully, we'll have the spaceport's control center on our side; it'll be able to guide us in, and to send tugs to assist us if necessary.",
